1. *Dani* su topli i sunčani. (The days are warm and sunny.)
2. U poslednjih nekoliko dana bilo je veoma hladno. (In the last few days it has been very cold.)
3. Često se sviđamo u *danima* kada smo umorni. (We often get along on days when we are tired.)
4. Uvek se budim rano ujutru u ponedeljak *danima*. (I always wake up early in the Monday mornings.)
5. *Dane* provedena sa prijateljima su najbolje. (Days spent with friends are the best.)